        <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary);">Telehealth anxiety psychology Sydney &mdash; related guides</strong>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <a href="/guides/telehealth-anxiety-psychology-sydney/" style="background: var(--color-accent-soft); border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-light); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-accent-hover); font-weight: 500;">Telehealth anxiety guide (pillar) &uarr;</a>
          <a href="/guides/clinical-psychologist-vs-registered-psychologist/" style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Clinical vs registered psychologist</a>
          <a href="/guides/mental-health-care-plan-sydney/" style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Getting a Mental Health Care Plan</a>
          <a href="/guides/how-to-choose-anxiety-psychologist-telehealth/" style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How to choose a psychologist</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>One of the most common questions people have when they start looking for mental health support is: should I see a psychologist or a psychiatrist? The short answer depends mostly on whether you are considering medication and whether your anxiety has been difficult to treat. This guide explains the differences in plain language so you can have an informed conversation with your GP.</p>

      <h2>At a Glance: Psychologist vs Psychiatrist</h2>

